          <title>
            <string language="en">"The Voting-Place."</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">"Der Wählen-Platz."</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">"Le Voter-Endroit."</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">"O Vot-Lugar."</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">"Il Vot-Posto."</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">"Η ψηφίζω-θέση."</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">"El Votar-Lugar."</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">During the 1840s and 1850s, anti-immigrant feelings grew amongst many native born whites. These nativists" argued that immigrants caused many of the nation's ills by rejecting "American" work habits</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Humanities</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Während des 1840s und des 1850s wuchsen Anti-Immigrant 
Gefühle unter vielem gebürtigem getragenem Weiß. Diese 
Nativists "argumentierten, daß Immigranten viele der Kranken der 
Nation verursachten, indem sie" amerikanische "Arbeit Gewohnheiten 
zurückwiesen</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Pendant le 1840s et le 1850s, les sentiments 
d'anti-immigré se sont développés parmi beaucoup de blancs soutenus
indigènes. Ces nativistes "ont argué du fait que les immigrés
ont causé plusieurs des défectuosités de la nation en rejetant 
habitudes" américaines des "de travail</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Durante o 1840s e o 1850s, os sentimentos do 
anti-anti-immigrant cresceram amongst muitos brancos carregados 
nativos. Estes nativists "discutiram que os immigrants causaram 
muitos dos mais da nação rejeitando hábitos" americanos do 
"trabalho</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Durante il 1840s ed il 1850s, le sensibilità 
dell'anti-immigrante si sono sviluppate fra molti bianchi sopportati 
natali. Questi nativists "hanno sostenuto che gli immigranti 
hanno causato molti dei ills della nazione rifiutando le abitudini" 
americane "del lavoro</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κατά τη διάρκεια του 1840s και του 1850s, τα 
αντι-που έχουν μεταναστεύσει συναισθήματα αυξήθηκαν μεταξύ 
πολλών εγγενών γεννημένων λευκών. Αυτά τα nativists 
"υποστήριξαν ότι οι μετανάστες προκάλεσαν πολλών από τα δεινά 
του έθνους με την απόρριψη" των αμερικανικών "συνηθειών εργασίας</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Durante el 1840s y el 1850s, las sensaciones del 
contra-inmigrante crecieron entre muchos blancos llevados nativos. 
Estos nativistas "discutieron que los inmigrantes causaran 
muchas de las enfermedades de la nación rechazando hábitos" 
americanos "del trabajo</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
